            "questionText": "A packaging company is designing boxes for a new electronics gadget that has a mass of $!$5.5\\,\\text{kg}$!$. Determine the weight of the gadget on a celestial body where the gravitational field strength is $!$2 \\times 9.8\\,\\text{N/kg}$!$.",
